summary: Even tho she has to scavenge to earn portions of portions, she doesn’t sell off a droid just trying to get back to its master...
caption:
Even tho she has to scavenge to earn portions of portions, she doesn’t sell off a droid just trying to get back to its master for enough food to sustain her for weeks if not months.
And after TLJ, you can see she might know what it’s like to be sold off.
